tiers.ability_description: Light Side allies have +100% Critical Chance while attacking out of turn.
At the start of each Rogue One ally's turn, if they have not taken damage since their last turn, they gain Critical Chance Up and Offense Up for 1 turn.
Whenever Jyn Erso critically hits an enemy, Jyn Erso gains 10% Critical Damage, Defense Penetration, and Offense (stacking, max 200%) until the end of battle.

Whenever K-2SO attacks out of turn, K-2SO deals 150% bonus damage, inflicts Offense Down and Healing Immunity for 1 turn on all enemies, which can't be evaded or resisted.
Whenever K-2SO loses Taunt, he removes 50% Turn Meter from all enemies and inflicts Blind on them for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

At the start of encounter, if Admiral Raddus is the ally in the Leader slot and all other allies are Rogue One, inflict Defense Down and Expose for 2 turns on all enemies, which can't be evaded or resisted. Whenever Admiral Raddus uses his Basic ability, he calls another random Rogue One ally to assist. Admiral Raddus can't be defeated while K-2SO is active.
At the beginning of their turn, Light Side allies have +25% chance to dispel all debuffs on themself.
Whenever enemies are damaged at the start of their turn, Unaligned Force User allies gain 2% Turn Meter.
Whenever Cere Junda uses a Basic ability on their turn, other allies gain +25% Turn Meter.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Critical Chance Up, Critical Damage Up, and Offense Up for 2 turns.
Whenever First Order allies Stun an enemy, they gain Speed Up and Offense Up for 2 turns and inflict Expose for 2 turns at the end of that turn, which can't be evaded.
Whenever another ally attacks during General Hux's turn, General Hux and that ally gain 25% Turn Meter (limit once per turn).
